*********** AWS CodePipeline (CI CD Pipeline) ***********

-> Use cases of AWS CodePipeline
1) Source
- AWS CodeCommit
- Amazon S3
	- Versioning
	- Monitoring
- Tool : GitHub , ECR
- Supports Git command
- GitHub Compatible
- Can migrate repos from GitHub
- Fully managed
- Scalable
- Secure
- Highly Available

2) Build
- AWS CodeBuild
- Tool : Jenkins
- Fully managed
- Scalable
- IAM
- Encryption

3) Deploy
- AWS CodeDeploy
- Tool : AWS CodeDeploy
- Services : ECS , EC2 , Elastic Beanstalk , Lambda
- Fully managed
- Scalable
- Minimizes downtime
- Centralized
- Automated deployments
- Simultaneous deploymnts

-> IAM Roles we need
1) AWSServiceRoleForAmazonSSM 
- AmazonSSMServiceRolePolicy

2) EC2InstanceRole 
- AmazonSSMManagedInstanceCore
- AmazonEC2RoleforAWSCodeDeploy

4) CodeDeployRole 
- AWSCodeDeployRole
